:Namespace ResolveSubfolderTests

‚ćĚ root ResolveSubfolder relFolder is the path-traversal gate: empty
‚ćĚ relFolder returns root unchanged; a valid child resolves to its real
‚ćĚ path; anything that canonicalises (following '.'/'..' and symlinks) to
‚ćĚ somewhere other than root itself or one of its real descendants comes
‚ćĚ back as 'outside-root', never a path. Fixtures live under
‚ćĚ tests/fixtures/resolve-subfolder/: root/ (with a real child sub/,
‚ćĚ sub/nested/, and evil-link - a committed symlink to ../outside), a
‚ćĚ sibling root-evil/ sharing root's name as a string prefix, and outside/
‚ćĚ - all real, since realpath needs every existing component to actually
‚ćĚ exist to prove the traversal/symlink cases are rejected for real.

    ‚ąá p‚ÜźFixturePath name
      p‚Üź#.AplServiceRoot,'tests/fixtures/resolve-subfolder/',name
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá root‚ÜźRoot
      root‚ÜźFixturePath'root'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderReturnsRootUnchangedForEmptyInput
      r‚Üź(Root)‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder''
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderResolvesValidChildSubfolder
      r‚Üź(FixturePath'root/sub')‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'sub'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderResolvesNestedValidSubfolder
      r‚Üź(FixturePath'root/sub/nested')‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'sub/nested'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderResolvesNonexistentSubfolderWithinRoot
    ‚ćĚ A subfolder that does not exist yet is a CheckFolder 'not-found'
    ‚ćĚ case, not a traversal attempt: ResolveSubfolder must still return a
    ‚ćĚ within-root path rather than 'outside-root'.
      r‚Üź(FixturePath'root/no-such-folder')‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'no-such-folder'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderRejectsParentTraversal
      r‚Üź'outside-root'‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'../../etc'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderRejectsAbsolutePathInput
      r‚Üź'outside-root'‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'/etc'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderRejectsSymlinkPointingOutsideRoot
      r‚Üź'outside-root'‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'evil-link'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźTest_ResolveSubfolderRejectsSiblingDirectorySharingRootNameAsPrefix
    ‚ćĚ root-evil is a real sibling of root; reaching it via '../root-evil'
    ‚ćĚ would wrongly pass a bare string-prefix check against root (no
    ‚ćĚ separator boundary), since 'root-evil' starts with 'root'.
      r‚Üź'outside-root'‚Č°Root #.ResolveSubfolder'../root-evil'
    ‚ąá

:EndNamespace
